President Trump held a press conference in the Oval Office where he discussed various topics including the 50th anniversary of the moon landing, the importance of space exploration for defense, and the role of private financing in the space industry. He also addressed the ongoing tension between the US and Iran, the debt ceiling, and his support for rapper A$AP Rocky. Additionally, he expressed his liking for Boris Johnson, the likely next British Prime Minister, and mentioned the tension between Japan and South Korea.